    BeanInitializer<ImageInitialization>

    public class SegmentMaskRCNN
extends SegmentFromTensorFlowModel
    Segments an image according a Mask-RCNN model with an Inception backbone trained on the COCO dataset.

    See the tutorial that provided inspiration.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
